result.name: the dining room

reviews.text: Nice environment, foods just acceptable ... and pricy as well

Stop by for lunch on a Sunday.  About 80% seated.  Mainly Shanghainese food.  Have tried their branches at Kowloon Bay and Aberdeen.  This one is a bit better than the other two.  Spent HK$377 for 3persons.
Stopped by the shop for a quick lunch. Its not the best, but the food, service and environment combined should have a higher rating than 2.7 (avg) at the time of the visit.
Mushrooms? Hahaha! It is not!

The dining room food is primarily Shanghainese. There are food items that are Sichuan food as well as Cantonese food as well. 

Food: 2.5 stars
Service/environment: 2 star
Value: 2 stars

I have eaten at the Kornhill location and the food at that restaurant is much better.  We had a mixture of snacks and main courses:

1) the pan fried buns (生煎包) are characterized as their specialty. These are probably the worst version I have had. I had trouble finishing one. 

2) the scallion pancake - this is good and I would recommend ordering it.

3) 小龙包 (soup dumplings) - this is below average. The meat and soup is lacking in flavour. 

4) fried yellow fish- I recommend ordering. The fish are fried nicely and was tasty. 

5) fried rice with shrimp- this is ok not bad but not great. 

6) green beans with minced pork- above average. Taste is right but a little greasy

7) potstickers- average dish. The skin was pan fried correctly but the meat lacked proper flavoring. Similar issue to the soup dumpling. 

My bill also included an item I didn’t order. I don’t think this was done on purpose but this definitely affected my perception of the service.

result.name: 南小館

reviews.text: 外面裝飾優雅，食物味道很不錯。
這一星針對這裡極差的服務質量，尤其是門口旁邊的女收銀員。說話語氣，面部表情都好似顧客跟她有仇似的。毫無禮貌。除此之外，其實飯菜有3星。小籠包包皮偏厚，擔擔麵缺少花生和芝麻醬。價錢也不便宜。作為在這商場行走過二十餘年的食客，這裡遠比以前同類餐廳的質量低。我個人建議：能免則免。
食物質素中上，會再光顧的餐館，推。
Nice environment, foods just acceptable ... and pricy as well
經濟實惠，環境舒適，服務好。

result.name: Discovery Park

reviews.text: Excellent place for family with kids. Can spend all day here with reasonable cost. Public facilities, shops and entertainment are all well designed with kids in mind. The cinema is even decorated and provided with kids seats and play areas. Coming place is more spacious than you could imagine.
Large mall with wide variety of shops, restaurants, and a cinema, but no supermarket. Great place for families with young kids. Parking is relatively cheap.
Good location, family friendly! Good for shopping with kids

A large and well designed shopping mall. Shops were of large types and properly located at different areas of the mall. Food choices were absurd with a bizarre choice from local fast food to American tastes to top-of-the-class cuisines. A huge recommendation for foodies. Activities there are also never-ending and makes the mall suitable for children and adults of all ages.
Spacious.  Good restaurants.  Convenient supermarket.  Comfortable weeknight visit.
